iYeah, you read me correctly. I'm saying that it doesn't matter if		gopher.black	70
ithere's no supernatural involved at all or if there is. The aim of		gopher.black	70
idivination is to seek to foresee the future or discover hidden		gopher.black	70
iknowledge and divination can succeed in  both cases regardless of		gopher.black	70
ithe origin of its power.		gopher.black	70
