iLets side with the pragmatic doubter practitioner for a moment and		gopher.black	70
iassume that there's no magic at work here at all. We're going to		gopher.black	70
igo through some exercise that will result in symbols ready for		gopher.black	70
iinterpretation. The process we have just taken was designed to		gopher.black	70
