ispending a significant amount of time in so doing. We are now		gopher.black	70
iasked to review and interpret these forms which have a variety of		gopher.black	70
ipossible meanings requiring we try to apply them systematically		gopher.black	70
iand in various combinations to the problem or subject. That		gopher.black	70
ithought process involves mental judo and an openness to new ideas.		gopher.black	70
iIt will inevitably bring insight and... wait for it... hidden		gopher.black	70
iknowledge. It will also undoubtedly influence future actions and		gopher.black	70
ihave a major impact on the events to come. BAM! Divined.		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iNow, allow yourself to take the seat as an individual who has		gopher.black	70
